Name: Fireboy & Watergirl: Fairy Tales
About the game: Fireboy & Watergirl are back. This time you'll have the help of the forest fairies to complete 30 new levels. In this platformer game you have to control both characters as well as the helping fairies in order to get to the finish doors of each level. Solve the puzzles, beat the times and collect all the diamonds! Play alone or with a friend to join Fireboy and Watergirl in this adventure!
